dct_title_s: Town plan of Reggio Emilia. G.S.G.S. 4380
dct_description_sm: Reprinted 1943 by A.M.S. 3-43. 114757. Military grid (brown). Grid provisional. Shows railways, tram lines, cable railways, roads, and province, district, and commune boundaries. United States. Army Map Service AMS 1. Reprinted 1943 by A.M.S. In upper left margin: Italy. Great Britain. War Office. General Staff. Geographical Section. G.S.G.S. no. 4380

[London] : War Office. General Staff. Geographical Section, 1943.
